Citation.sTitle: Measurement and Correlation for Solubility of 11alpha-Hydroxy-16alpha,17alpha-epoxyprogesterone and 16alpha,17alpha-Epoxyprogesterone in Solvents
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of 11a-hydroxy-16a,17a-epoxyprogesterone and 16a,17a-epoxyprogesterone in isopropanol, n-propanol, DMSO, dioxane, and 1-butanol have been determined. A solubility model is proposed, and the solubilities calculated by the model show good agreement with experimental data.
